  "instructions": [
    "Sauté the onion and garlic in olive oil until softened.",
    "Add the cabbage, raisins, pistachios, cinnamon, allspice, salt, and sugar to the pan and cook until the cabbage is tender.",
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Assemble the briouat by layering the cabbage mixture between sheets of phyllo dough.",
    "Brush the top of the briouat with olive oil.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the phyllo is golden brown."
